definitions.definition: Ellipsis of Crecy-en-Ponthieu : a commune and village in Somme department, Hauts-de-France , France .
Ellipsis of Crecy Forest : a forest in Somme department, Hauts-de-France , France .
Ellipsis of Crecy Campaign , a military campaign during the Hundred Years War in 1346 .
Ellipsis of Battle of Crecy , a battle in 1346 during the Crecy Campaign in the Hundred Years War .
